The paper deals with a natural language processing task of question answering, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The model proposed in the paper involves reasoning and decision-making processes, which are typical of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) subfields. The model also utilizes a knowledge base, which is a common feature of information retrieval (cs.IR) and database (cs.DB) research.
